Maintainer: seonghobae <seonghobae@users.noreply.github.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/seonghobae/rclone-azureblob-airgap

Package: rclone-azureblob-airgap
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: rclone + Azure Blob Storage airgap bootstrap for Ubuntu
  Provides rclone binary, bundled FUSE3 runtime bootstrap payloads,
 configuration templates, systemd service units, and helper scripts for
 deploying rclone with Azure Blob Storage mount support on air-gapped Ubuntu
 VMs (22.04/24.04) behind Azure Private Link.
 .
 Features:
  - rclone v1.73.2 binary (amd64/arm64)
  - Bundled FUSE3 runtime bootstrap via postinst (jammy/noble x amd64/arm64)
  - Azure Blob authentication templates (Account Key, SAS, SP, MSI)
  - systemd mount service template (rclone-azureblob@.service)
  - Interactive configuration helper and verification scripts
  - disable_instance_discovery support for Private Link environments
